[package]
name = "msg_parser"
description = "Outlook Email Message (.msg) parser"
version = "0.1.2"
authors = ["Marirs <marirs@gmail.com>"]
readme = "README.md"
license = "MIT"
categories = ["email", "parser-implementations"]
keywords = ["msg", "mail", "ole", "outlook", "parser"]
repository = "https://github.com/marirs/msg-parser-rs"
homepage = "https://github.com/marirs/msg-parser-rs"
edition = "2018"

[dependencies]
regex = "1"
serde_json = "1"
thiserror = "1"

[dependencies.hex]
version = "0.4"
features = ["serde"]

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1"
features = ["derive"]

[lib]
name = "msg_parser"
path = "src/lib.rs"

[badges.travis-ci]
repository = "marirs/msg-parser-rs"

[profile.dev]
opt-level = 3

[profile.release]
codegen-units = 1
debug-assertions = false
debug = false
opt-level = 3
lto = true
